{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b8adf70967","title":"对军队同志的教导","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4a898a098c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"b8adf70967"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2d982b4677","type":"title","text":"对军队同志的教导","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"b8adf70967"},{"id":"6e6d1bd5ad","type":"paragraph","text":"有了错误就检讨就改正，改了就好了，只要讲三句话就行了。一句话：错了：二句话：是什么错就是什么错，在这个问题上或那个问题上是方向错了就承认这个问题上方向错了；第三句话：就改正。这样就好了。公开检查比不公开好，高姿态检查比低姿态好，早检查比晚检查好。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"b8adf70967"},{"id":"5346e02a07","type":"paragraph","text":"军队这几年群众工作做得少，错了改了就好，也不给处分，也不要治罪。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"b8adf70967"}],"page":{"id":"b96f29b67d","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"b8adf70967","start":32,"end":32}}}},"__N_SSG":true}